  "title": "Order & Admin Support",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Handling and processing of customer orders.</li><li>Data entry of orders into the system.</li><li>Communicating with customers on order matters.</li><li>Attending to customer requests and enquiries.</li><li>Coordinating with internal teams to ensure smooth order fulfilment.</li><li>Providing general administrative support to maintain good customer relations.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Good communication and interpersonal skills.</li><li>Careful and accurate in data entry.</li><li>Able to handle multiple tasks and meet deadlines.</li><li>Basic computer knowledge (Google Sheet, email, WhatsApp).</li><li>Able to start work immediately</li></ul><p><strong>Work Location: </strong>Office-based</p><ul><li>Report to office daily</li><li>12:30 AM – 5:30 PM (Monday to Friday)</li></ul>",
